{"tid":2414943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook收取中國官媒廣告費，淡化新疆種族滅絕行為","createTime":"2021-02-19T21:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T19:52:33.000Z","uid":256837,"like":152,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"639d2ed29ac12dfdf68addbf3b05b8a85fa86f2f","tid":2414943,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T21:57:59.000Z","msg":"Profits from propaganda: Facebook takes China cash to promote Uyghur disinformation<br />\n<br />\nFacebook is taking money from China to promote &ldquo;propaganda&rdquo; playing down the plight of Uyghur Muslims, a Press Gazette investigation has found. <br />\n<br />\nUS social media giant Facebook has not only allowed state-run outlets like China Daily and CGTN to publish posts that dismiss these concerns as Western &ldquo;disinformation&rdquo; &ndash; it has accepted advertising payments to help promote this content to millions of people<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvEx0GS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvEx0GS.png&h=44345970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://pressgazette.co.uk/facebook-china-misinformation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpressgazette.co.uk%2Ffacebook-china-misinformation%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=6711c608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pressgazette.co.uk/facebook-china-misinformation/</a>"},{"pid":"aab3ad6084dbe384e0e847aee1a5086bed3b2f6f","tid":2414943,"uid":250082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T22:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563e2a95029a171c2bbb5a76139128ec09c4aae7","tid":2414943,"uid":206594,"like":45,"dislike":4,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T22:30:15.000Z","msg":"淡化新疆種族滅絕行為<br />\n明明係班liberal共識來<br />\n講到十惡不赦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22af1fdd146ed5498